criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients over 18 years;

          -  patients of any sex, race, age, who have accepted to participate in the study by
             signing the informed consent form of the study.

          -  patients with surgical wounds to treat thoracic-abdominal aortic pathology.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with established sepsis;

          -  patients with septic recurrence;

          -  patients with sensitivity to silver.
